    <item>
      <title>About Peace Or The Peace</title>
      <link>https://dasarpai.com/wiaposts/about-peace-or-the-peace/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jun 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>https://dasarpai.com/wiaposts/about-peace-or-the-peace/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://dasarpai.com/assets/images/wiapost/5020-About-Peace-Or-The-Peace.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;About Peace Or The Peace&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;About Peace Or The Peace 
    &lt;div id=&#34;about-peace-or-the-peace&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#about-peace-or-the-peace&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Peace and happiness in life is a desire of every human.  &lt;br&gt;
Is it a goal of life, which we shall achieve one day?  &lt;br&gt;
If you don’t have it then it may be a goal for you.  &lt;br&gt;
Otherwise it a basic requirement of a human.  &lt;br&gt;
We want to talk peacefully, eat peacefully,  &lt;br&gt;
walk peacefully, sleep peacefully, and whatnot.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
